question: So here's my thoughts on your poat.  100% agree with you that the Cyrus discovering himself storyline has been done well and also agree that the look back edit  (which was classic hype building) and apple cider scene were not  needed but.... idk I think the fact the bulk of Tyrus is in 3C and TJ is only in 3 episodes could be a letdown
answer: I’m not quite sure what you mean? When you say “the bulk of Tyrus is in 3c” are you referring to the bulk of them together as a couple? Because I feel like their storyline has been spread out fairly well over the course of the series overall. But if you’re referring to strictly-romantic Tyrus, then yes - it’s obviously going to be confined to the final episodes. But that’s part of what makes it a good slow burn ship. The idea that we’ve watched these two people who we know are supposed to be together, but they aren’t aware of it yet, and then in their final moments on screen together they become aware of it?? That is some quality shit. Basically what I’m saying is, it’s all about perspective. It’s only a “let down” if you have expectations that are high enough to be let down. Would I love to spend more time with TJ’s character before the finale? Would I love to see their relationship continue after the finale? Of course! But I don’t think that the fact that those things aren’t happening is automatically going to make their storyline a “let down”. If I’m disappointed after the finale, you guys will be the first to know. But for now, I have faith in Terri and the cast to trust that when we are told that we won’t be disappointed, that they’re right.

summary: First Date (1 swear word so dont report me) 😤 BTW This is a bit connected to my Thrift Store Fic coming up
body:
First Date (1 swear word so dont report me) 😤 BTW This is a bit connected to my Thrift Store Fic coming up

To Say TJ Kippen was nervous was the biggest understatement of the year, he had spent 30 minutes pacing his bedroom floor, switching outfits as fast as politicians switch sides, his hands were pouring rivers of sweat, his mind was racing and Amber comments from across the hall about TJ not needing to worry amd that Cyrus will love him in anything had the opposite effect to which TJ would remind her about her own clothing delamia with Andi which would shut her up.

Ding Dong “Crap” Cyrus was here, TJ looked at the mirror one last time ofcourse the colors of his suit didn’t compilment any of his feature and he looked awful but he couldnt leave Cyrus waiting so he put some more gel in his hair, grabbed the pinic basket and raced down the stairs.

“Hey Underdog You look amazing ” TJ smiled, he turned to see a gorgeous Cyrus wearing a pale irish green button up polo and khakis

“Hi TJ and Thanks” Cyrus smiled back feeling a little self conscious compared to TJs Navy blue suit, with a purple and gray striped Tie. “You know you dont look to bad yourself” TJ boushed Cyrus thought he looked good yes.

“Ready to go” TJ held Cyrus hand realsiing what he did he stammred “Is this okay”

Cyrus laughed sweetly “It more than okay” he held on tighter, TJ calmed down a little bit and color returned to his face “Dont be so nervous that my job” Cyrus nuged TJ and grinned

“Im-m not nervous, Just a little bit over existed” TJ lied biting his lip “Why did i do something wrong”

“Not nervous huh” Cyrus raised his eyebrow

“Shut Up” TJ rolles his eyes

“Make me” TJ grinned mishcivously and gave Cyrus a quick peck, Cyrus smiled and they walked along the grey sidewalk occasionally kicking spare rocks that sprung out of the gravel the cold air creating a deadly silence

“So not so nervous basketball guy were are you kidnapping me to” They both laughed

“The Swing set” TJ suggested

“How cliche, which ya novel did you get that from”

“Delirum” TJ grinned “but come on you know you love it”TJ teased

“Not as much as I love you” Cyrus mumbled he gave TJ a kiss on the cheek which was as far as he could reach

“I love you to”

“Who doesnt”

“Hey there only room for one ego in this relationship” TJ smiled

“Im sorry forgive me King Kippen” Cyrus mockingly bowed down on the cold gravel, waving his hands up and down

“That King Goodman to you” TJ smirked he put his arm around Cyrus and inched closer to him filling in the one ceminter gap between them

“Awww that was kind of smooth” Cyrus smiles he looked up to the night sky just above the park entrance “Hey Teej look at the stars” Cyrus pointed up to the dark blue sky were there were two stars close together shinig brighlty, Cyrus smiled in awe “Thier beautiful”

“Not as much as you” TJ mumbled he grabbed Cyrus towards thier swing set and layed the pinic blanket with a choclate chip muffin painted on it under the tall grass, TJ layed down on the blanket

“So whats for dinner honey” Cyrus smirked he put his head on TJ leg and cutting off his blood circulation TJ didnt mind though TJ laughed

“Not even a how was your day” Cyrus shoved TJ

“How was your day and what for dinner”

“It was amazing I learned this new recipe and Janet from the PTA liked my cookies” TJ said as he made his voice sound feminine “And for dinner your favorite hand baked Choclate Chip Muffins and for dessert I made fried rice with a side of chicken mac and cheese with a special drink ” TJ got out a plastic food bag holding all of the muffins and handed Cyrus a muffin, he set out the paper plates and scooped out some of the food making sure to give Cyrus the majority of the choclate chip muffins and fried rice while he greedily took most of the blueberry macadamia.

“You know I only date you for your cooking skills” Cyrus smirked he ate another 2 dozen muffins and sighed he was in heaven TJ shook his head and poured Cyrus some sparkling lemonade

“I know” TJ grabbed Cyrus shoulders and kissed him on the lips and Cyrus blushed

Another Bad One shot by your truly yes Ofcourse (I improved TJ fashion sense your all welcome, because I will kill disney more if Tj and Cyrus first date starts with TJ wearing a hoodie) also sorry this is long but 😎 just read it cue me dancing to just beat it but with just read it lyrics ( this was funnier in my head like all my attempts at writing comedy new flash it never funny) also I stan Confident Cyrus and Nervous TJ Edit Because I spelled blushed wrong yeet

summary: If you were Buffy, would you have thrown away the shoes Walker made you?
question: If you were Buffy, would you have thrown away the shoes Walker made you?
answer:
No I wouldn’t. In her situation, since she was intending to end the relationship I’d have returned the shoes (like Andi tries to do). It would be a waste of his time for her to just throw them away.

I get that it wasn’t so personal since he already did it for Andi but he’s artistic it’s the type of thing he does it would be like if Andi made a bracelet for her next SO. Like yeah she did thay for Jonah too but it’s actually still personalised to them it’s just her kind of craft?

It’s just rude imo. I know where she is coming from but I don’t agree with her response 🤷🏼‍♀️

question: CCCMs or blueberry macademia?
answer:
Depends on the mood

Like I bloody love a good CCCM but sometimes it’s not such a sweet tooth moment and Blunerry is genuinely my second choice plus the nut would make an interesting extra flavour.

So I’d say generally CCCM

Now if this question is a code for TJ or Cyrus 😏😏😏

I think TJ edges it over for me like I love my gay sons with all my heart and Cyrus is legit a mood with the clumsiness and self doubt. And he is so forgiving and believing in people when others won’t and that’s amazing

But something about TJ like he’s also full of the self doubt but also a secret dork and he messes up a lot but he’s working on it and I love him. He’s not perfect and I love that. He deserves the world he is precious and he can’t catch a break. He doesn’t have the support Cyrus has and I wanna send TJ Kippen all my love
